{"tid":1930174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益］一人幾句給區議員的建議/ 鼓勵","createTime":"2020-03-17T11:18:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T03:51:57.000Z","uid":20442,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b908c00f2dfc73cad56d4448a10c8e8366cb4383","tid":1930174,"uid":20442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:18:25.000Z","msg":"區議員要有覺悟，簡單講下目標：<br />\n<br />\n1. 證明本土派 》尸位素餐的民建聯、鄉黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 擴大黄絲光譜，證明後生有心有力，做實事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 「本土」派就係本地市民民生行先，以香港更適宜人住為目標。<br />\n<br />\n手段/ 議題： <br />\n<br />\n1. 了解老人家，陪傾、噓寒問暖，搵出無良老人院、幫下佢哋生活困難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 重複民建聯所為： 蛇齋餅糭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.搞義工團隊，服務社區，搵和理非、大媽做，謝絕勇武，真係要幫人，例如：整揮春、幫買餸、陪覆診。<br />\n<br />\n4.研究交通，重整路線，多人合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 研究棕土，推動活化土地，search 姚松炎、朱凱迪就有前人source，多人合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n6.收集意見，因時制宜： 搞衛生（捉老鼠）、整紅綠燈、天橋、加下圍欄、垃圾桶⋯⋯要有用，唔係大笨象<br />\n<br />\n7. 幫下窮人、兒童，補習又好、sim卡上網又好、自修室又好、二手贈送物資（大褸、電腦）又好⋯⋯ <br />\n<br />\n8. 你多啲請教人⋯⋯ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n民建制做咗反對黨，佢哋唔想你哋做到嘢，贏民心，區議員就要利用人多勢眾，做大量民生事務，唔係做失敗撚⋯⋯⋯ 亦唔好日日搞敏感議題，俾藍絲玩「泥漿摔角」，浪費「上位機會」（證明老一代冇心冇力）<br />\n嗱，不過要知彼知己，<br />\n<br />\n傳統派別缺點：<br />\n老派泛民被指責出賣香港人、不做實事；<br />\n建制少數派就投票機器，不會為香港本地人、後生謀出路。<br />\n<br />\n生存技能：<br />\n老派泛民：會屌下政府，但止於此<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（垃圾）<br />\n建制派：搞下民生，打下關係（佢哋幫到好多老人、基層）<br />\n<br />\n因此，本土派區議員要集百家大成：<br />\n1.搞好民生而旗幟鮮明（有啲位都要同政府合作，你哋先有錢起橋修路）<br />\n2.做到父母官，引到更多後生建設社會係最高目標，退一步，出糧架，盡做ok？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 要識「領功」/ 經營facebook，整banner、通俾人聽你點幫過人⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n黄絲要學識執政，聆聽市民訴求，有別777，亦唔係投票機器，呢個先係我哋願望⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n分享吓我睇電視見到嘅好主意：<br />\n<br />\n1.我睇過「老人陪老人覆診」，儲鐘數，搵義工做記錄、中間人，啲鐘數等佢哋要人幫助時，再搵人幫佢哋。<br />\n陳伯陪張伯覆診3 小時； 我哋幫陳伯大掃除3 小時。<br />\n<br />\n成個系統好多記錄，儲卡仔，啲老人家好鍾意「儲時數」<br />\n<br />\n2.搞靚啲公屋燈飾，而唔係垃圾大笨象<br />\n<br />\nps 民建聯等妖孽潛伏在旁，嘈生晒，其實係提醒你哋前進嘅動力！加油！ 可以有不同意見，但唔可以傷和氣，重大議題要一致步伐！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nps2 藍絲、民建聯妖孽會破壞你、侮辱你，但請你以高EQ 輾壓佢哋，多啲為社區付出（一定要俾人知道）<br />\n<br />\n以下開放俾大家認真擺低幾句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如小弟有講錯嘢，請大家原諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dd757662aecc05218a78f1f11e4b72916eb23ae","tid":1930174,"uid":128817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:19:56.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b46c539e10be29d25d4aa8491d829b3eaad3c900","tid":1930174,"uid":20442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:21:42.000Z","msg":"出post 源於見到隔離篇《我推咗個垃圾入區議會》<br />\n<br />\n覺得預期放負，不如拋磚引玉⋯⋯ <br />\n<br />\n黄店、黄議員都會經歷進進出出、汰弱留強，有人做唔到、唔識做、自我中心，但一定有唔少有心人跑出，政治上接棒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />世界就係咁"},{"pid":"a09509539b4903508b731432ad3dd03b9ba20c38","tid":1930174,"uid":20442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:24:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幫手留言，叫下五大訴求，缺一不可都好"},{"pid":"717e0c5a0c4cf17a22a5e6176950f940d0bd95cc","tid":1930174,"uid":20442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:24:51.000Z","msg":"認真posts 求集氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e45292bac8d27c1a6134e2f74ba6863fa399115f","tid":1930174,"uid":20442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:26:00.000Z","msg":"在職人士，不妨一人一句啦<br />\n<br />\n讀書嘅，都講下邊區有咩睇法<br />\n<br />\n一齊前行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f26846a1207868e427fcf8608ca31cf08c0693f","tid":1930174,"uid":20442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:27:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"624fc01e61ebc9246c712061d8a2bad91b98e77a","tid":1930174,"uid":258217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:28:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好玩膠，做實事</span>"},{"pid":"c1d26a1be8df4df11e26fafce4ec1d44befbe7a7","tid":1930174,"uid":20442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:29:30.000Z","msg":"721 831 101"},{"pid":"11b5de43dc6538e1fa95c21e505b2c57a761057f","tid":1930174,"uid":20442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:33:38.000Z","msg":"認真posts 冇市場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40f96371b5cd27364984da4a874181e8857e2b75","tid":1930174,"uid":163499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:34:02.000Z","msg":"有個問題係<br />\n政府係撚咁削佢地權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"227cb6d8c2caf3eb0520e5ce1a86ac9cfa115157","tid":1930174,"uid":20442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40f96371b5cd27364984da4a874181e8857e2b75","tid":1930174,"uid":163499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:34:02.000Z","msg":"有個問題係<br />\n政府係撚咁削佢地權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:37:02.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過新官上任一定預咗俾人搞，個位要坐暖，要靠佢哋自己俾啲力。<br />\n<br />\n有少少建設，就會有bargaining power"},{"pid":"93a27a506894cf73049e0e0dfb25ffe82f5af161","tid":1930174,"uid":250654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T12:05:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"71b3dcba9df6256546ae1504550f1d2d5e5f5c9e","tid":1930174,"uid":20442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93a27a506894cf73049e0e0dfb25ffe82f5af161","tid":1930174,"uid":250654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T12:05:38.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T12:06:01.000Z","msg":"多謝師兄"},{"pid":"b77d27599852fa833dadc51a21fb05f0dd79ea9b","tid":1930174,"uid":250654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T12:07:59.000Z","msg":"區議員係一個好好嘅身份去吸納中老年人支持<br />\n中老年人思維好簡單<br />\n你幫到佢，令佢生活更方便就會支持"},{"pid":"286d552c287426414ea4f999fab7baf1ee137dcf","tid":1930174,"uid":250654,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T12:10:02.000Z","msg":"雖然好柒<br />\n但適量「成功爭取」banner 好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n增加區議員自己嘅曝光率"},{"pid":"01c259413ad67b7775765894dcfd262de6970597","tid":1930174,"uid":20442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T12:12:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n認真求大家留句言，講下建議/ 鼓勵<br />\n<br />\n咩區有咩問題，俾位啲區議員上"},{"pid":"1a566bb706a8c2abfa88759f3cc4f69a411f0d62","tid":1930174,"uid":20442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T12:28:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a6f8bd2c03ea3a3a81ecc46ab293ecda206c67b","tid":1930174,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T12:51:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bb2a66238590a15c895e1dfff49d259357c14eba","tid":1930174,"uid":269202,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T12:56:21.000Z","msg":"建議：有能力既，成立一個中央政助群組<br />\n<br />\n轉介/ 集中處理專門民生問題，跟進及加大力度遣責政府不作為情況，個案可以分開處理，但追究可以一齊來，一個區議員可能因力量有限而未必就單一議題開記者會，十個？二十個？<br />\n<br />\n例如： 樓宇維修及水務工程，大廈鄰里關係問題<br />\n<br />\n以訓練人才及打造專業形象。<br />\n<br />\n地區工作，要深耕細作"},{"pid":"a0edf36e490ad6e060bdcd694343bd4c37dc3c23","tid":1930174,"uid":20442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb2a66238590a15c895e1dfff49d259357c14eba","tid":1930174,"uid":269202,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T12:56:21.000Z","msg":"建議：有能力既，成立一個中央政助群組<br />\n<br />\n轉介/ 集中處理專門民生問題，跟進及加大力度遣責政府不作為情況，個案可以分開處理，但追究可以一齊來，一個區議員可能因力量有限而未必就單一議題開記者會，十個？二十個？<br />\n<br />\n例如： 樓宇維修及水務工程，大廈鄰里關係問題<br />\n<br />\n以訓練人才及打造專業形象。<br />\n<br />\n地區工作，要深耕細作"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T13:45:34.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb821cc82b30c788a60c1c48f2844855c7409273","tid":1930174,"uid":160637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T13:52:40.000Z","msg":"推 營聚社區 連結公園啊伯 鄉音啊嬸"},{"pid":"d5f51f13bf9055725dd59c53e165292c955b27a0","tid":1930174,"uid":83177,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T13:56:15.000Z","msg":"見到區議員最近撲物資、派防疫用品好辛苦。<br />\n想話去做下義工幫手。佢又話親力親為好重要，有需要會主動請義工。<br />\n但到依家都冇消息。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你畀我哋街坊幫下手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cdd82e42a08ef6277039d0d1fd5d3b8821adb9e","tid":1930174,"uid":20442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T13:58:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 謝兩位"},{"pid":"0bedbec5d1f534663342843696de7dadf72f29c8","tid":1930174,"uid":307178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T14:24:25.000Z","msg":"推呀 P牌仔推唔郁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}